                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5804" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0874</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8284 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无可奈何花落去，似曾相识燕归来 ——“主动退市第一股”ST 国重装的回归之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Flowers fall off, do what one way, Swallows seem to be no strangers return. ——“The first delisting stock” ST Sinomach Heavy Equipment returned to the stock market</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李唯滨，刘金奇，冯玲玲，饶琦璇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨商业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国机重型装备集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">主动退市；重新上市；退市制度；ST 国重装</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Active delisting;Relisting; Delisting system; ST Sinomach Heavy Equipment</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">为了完善上市公司的退市制度，中国证监于2014年2月7日公布了《关于改革完善并严格实施上市公司退市制度的若干意见》。该意见首次强调了主动退市机制。而*ST二重也于次年申请主动退市，成为我国历史上的“主动退市第一股”。经过五年的退市整改，*ST二重更名为ST国重装并于2020年6月8日正式重新上市。本案例为描述型案例，对ST国重装（原*ST二重）的主动退市、整改与重新上市之路进行了梳理，描述了ST国重装为重新上市所进行的债务重组和资本运作的过程，并对我国资本市场退市制度的发展提出了相关建议，从投资者的视角对企业的投资价值进行了评价。通过本案例的学习，使学生能够结合具体经营状况对企业进行财务分析与评价，同时对资本运营中的企业上市、退市、重新上市等制度与方法进行了解。本案例对当前我国资本市场退市制度发展以及企业资本运作具有一定启发借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On February 7, 2014, the China Securities Regulatory Commission announced &quot;Several Opinions on Reforming, Perfecting and Strictly Implementing the Delisting System for Listed Companies,&quot; which will go into effect from November 16, 2014. The Opinions for the first time emphasized the voluntary delisting mechanism.And the *ST Erzhong also applied for voluntary delisting in the following year, becoming &quot;the first delisting stork&quot; in Chinese history.After five years of rectification, the *ST Erzhong was renamed the ST Sinomach Heavy Equipment and officially re-listed on June 8, 2020.This case is a descriptive case. It sorts out the path of active delisting, rectification and re-listing of ST Sinomach Heavy Equipment (formerly *ST Erzhong), describes the process of debt restructuring and capital operation of ST Sinomach Heavy Equipment for re-listing, and puts forward relevant
2 suggestions on the development of my country&#39;s capital market delisting system, and evaluates the investment value of the enterprise from the perspective of investors.Through the study of this case, students will be able to conduct financial analysis and evaluation of the company based on specific operating conditions, and at the same time learn about the systems and methods of corporate listing, delisting, and relisting in capital operations. This case has important inspiration and reference significance for the current development of my country&#39;s capital market delisting system and corporate capital operation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《高级财务管理理论与实务》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务分析与评价、退市、重新上市、债务重组、资产重组</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
